text: Phoebemima theaphia is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1881. It is known from Brazil and Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Phoebemima theaphia. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Hemilophini Category:Beetles described in 1881
title: Phoebemima theaphia
